&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are interested in every qualified candidate who is eligible to work in the United States. However, we are not able to sponsor visas or take over sponsorship at this time.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-ownership role at the center of how Enova Studios operates. We&#39;re rapidly evolving and want an operations leader who knows how to bridge Creative Ops and DesignOps, owning the systems, tools and processes that keep creative production and product/UX design moving. You’ll work in close partnership with the Head of Studios to set priorities, surface risks and drive the operational roadmap. You&#39;ll be the connective tissue between Studios and the broader business, leading cross-functional conversations and managing vendor relationships in ways that build visibility for the work and the people behind it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Enova Studios&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enova Studios is the in-house creative agency for Enova&#39;s small business and consumer lending brands: OnDeck, CashNetUSA, NetCredit, Simplic and more. We bring Creative, Content, Code and UX capabilities together under one roof. Leveraging deep brand knowledge, cross-functional relationships and strategic context, we turn customer insights into work that drives real results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About you &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Are you the kind of person who looks at a broken process and sees a design solution? Do you know the difference between a sprint and a production cycle and when each one applies? If you&#39;re energized by building smarter systems and helping creative and design teams do their best work, this role could be a great fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You know how creative and design teams work — the rhythms, the handoffs, the places where things quietly fall apart. You know how to build systems that hold. You&#39;re organized without being rigid. You&#39;re comfortable holding the line with stakeholders when the process calls for it and just as comfortable rolling up your sleeves when the team needs it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll own the operational infrastructure and execution of Enova Studios: reporting, traffic, tools, process and vendor management. You’ll build the systems and visibility that keep the team running, growing and accountable for results.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Objectives:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work is organized, moving and unblocked across all Studios capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leadership has clear visibility into project status and operational health&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Studios runs on a connected, well-maintained tool stack that account for marketing and product/UX design workflows alike&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;External relationships are well-managed and held to Studios standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Studios is always looking at what&#39;s next in tools and AI, not just what&#39;s working now&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain dashboards that surface the true state of work and inform decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end traffic management: ensuring work is captured, prioritized, resourced and tied back to measurable impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Studios managers on workflow, capacity and accountability so the team stays focused on execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Step in as project manager on larger initiatives, comfortable running a sprint or a traditional project depending on what the work requires&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as primary administrator of Asana and lead integration across the Studios tool stack, owning configuration, automations and ongoing optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; São Paulo, Brazil&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enova Overview:&lt;/strong&gt; Enova International (NYSE: ENVA) is a leading provider of online financial services for non-prime consumers and small businesses. With annual revenue of nearly $2 billion, we leverage advanced technology and analytics to serve millions of customers across the U.S. and Brazil. In Brazil, we operate as Simplic, offering 100% online personal loans with fast, flexible, and convenient access to credit. We combine the agility of a fast-growing startup with the stability of a large corporation, and we value smart, driven people who bring fresh, innovative ideas to the table.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role:&lt;/strong&gt; We are looking for an enthusiastic &lt;strong&gt;Data Analytics Intern&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Business team. Your mission will be to learn and assist our analysts in transforming data into insights, supporting areas such as Marketing, Credit, and Collections. We are seeking someone passionate about data, eager to learn and develop skills in SQL, Excel, and Python, while collaborating with different teams to generate real business impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in building queries and routine analyses to answer business questions and support the team in areas such as Marketing, Collections, and Credit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the creation and maintenance of performance dashboards and reports, ensuring they are clear and up-to-date.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help document processes, code, and analyses to facilitate teamwork.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shadow senior analysts and collaborate with Product, Operations, and Business teams to understand metrics and business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explore and learn new tools, techniques, and methodologies under the mentorship of our senior team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements and Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be currently pursuing a degree in Computer Science, Engineering, Statistics, Mathematics, Physics, Economics, or related fields &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge or strong academic interest in Python or R.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity and familiarity with statistics concepts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Eagerness to learn databases (SQL) and data manipulation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intermediate to Advanced English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactivity, organization, and a strong eagerness to learn.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits &amp;amp; Perks:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive Internship Stipend (&lt;em&gt;Bolsa Auxílio&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meal Voucher (&lt;em&gt;Vale Refeição&lt;/em&gt;) and Transportation Voucher (&lt;em&gt;Vale Transporte&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
