&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance, mentorship, and oversight to Tech Leads and engineers, particularly during incident resolution and complex project work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and evangelize Enova-wide design principles and coding standards to ensure consistently high-quality technical solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide perspective on leading industry trends and offer insight into emerging technologies relevant to the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
